jp.pay.android.ui.widget

クラス PayjpAcceptedBrandsView

  • jp.pay.android.ui.widget.PayjpAcceptedBrandsView

  • public class PayjpAcceptedBrandsView

    List of enum CardBrand logo. You can use this to display card acceptance. It will only show logos which provided by PayjpAcceptedBrandsView.setAcceptedBrands.

    関連項目:
    enum CardBrand, PayjpAcceptedBrandsView.setAcceptedBrands
